{"type":"message","id":"f69b9454","parentId":"8961770d","timestamp":"2026-03-06T01:02:33.234Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ShiHzzQZyjgpYFzEtc3dd6D4|fc_0572d43a1c78b9cd0169aa27a865ac81a19b832aac541b9fa5","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 量化交易自动化工作流配置\n\n## 定时任务\n\n### 1. 早盘任务 (9:00 交易日)\n```bash\npython3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/morning_scan.py\n```\n- 更新实时行情\n- 筛选候选股票\n- 生成交易信号\n- 发送日报\n\n### 2. 午后任务 (14:00 交易日)\n```bash\npython3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/afternoon_check.py\n```\n- 信号确认\n- 调仓准备\n- 风险检查\n\n### 3. 周优化 (周五 20:00)\n```bash\npython3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/weekly_optimize.py\n```\n- 策略复盘\n- 参数优化\n- 生成周报\n\n## 手动任务\n\n### 获取实时数据\n```bash\npython3 -c \"import akshare as ak; print(ak.stock_zh_a_spot_em())\"\n```\n\n### 选股\n```bash\npython3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/select_stocks.py\n```\n\n### 回测\n```bash\npython3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/backtest.py\n```\n\n## 告警配置\n\n### 止损告警\n- 单票亏损 > 8%\n\n### 暴涨告警\n- 单日涨幅 > 9%\n\n### 大盘告警\n- 大盘跌幅 > 3%\n\n## 通知渠道\n\n### 飞书通知\n- 配置飞书机器人 WebHook\n\n### 邮件通知\n- 配置 SMTP\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772758953232}}
