{"type":"message","id":"844cc73a","parentId":"06d9b792","timestamp":"2026-03-06T01:05:09.506Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_YJKzioyZy5AUlBe9nSDZ1sTS|fc_0572d43a1c78b9cd0169aa28444d1881a1a58350843312538f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"```\n\n---\n\n## 五、具体配置\n\n### 1. 安装所需工具\n```bash\n# 安装 uv (Python包管理)\nbrew install uv\n\n# 安装 Python 量化库\nuv pip install akshare backtrader pandas numpy\n```\n\n### 2. 配置自动化任务\n```yaml\n# cron 任务配置\ntasks:\n  - name: morning_scan\n    time: \"0 9 * * 1-5\"\n    command: python ~/openclaw/workspace/scripts/morning_scan.py\n    \n  - name: evening_review\n    time: \"0 15 * * 1-5\"\n    command: python ~/openclaw/workspace/scripts/evening_review.py\n    \n  - name: weekly_optimize\n    time: \"0 20 * * 5\"\n    command: python ~/openclaw/workspace/scripts/weekly_optimize.py\n```\n\n### 3. 设置监控告警\n- 止损触发告警\n- 选股信号通知\n- 策略异常提醒\n\n---\n\n## 六、预期效果\n\n| 指标 | 目标 |\n|------|------|\n| 年化收益 | 20%+ |\n| 夏普比率 | 1.0+ |\n| 最大回撤 | <20% |\n| 交易频率 | 每周1-2次 |\n| 自动化程度 | 90%+ |\n\n---\n\n## 七、下一步行动\n\n1. ✅ 技能已安装\n2. ⬜ 配置数据源 (AkShare)\n3. ⬜ 部署自动化脚本\n4. ⬜ 设置定时任务\n5. ⬜ 接入实盘(可选)\n\n---\n\n需要我帮你配置哪个模块？建议从**数据模块**开始，先把数据跑通。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772759109504}}
